SUMMARY:GRACS x NVIDIA: Building the Hardware Behind AI featuring Sr. Director David Brown
LOCATION:GDC 6.302 (Faculty Lounge)
DESCRIPTION:This event has been rescheduled to Wednesday, March 25 at 4:00 PM.\\n\\nDavid will give a talk about his team (ASCII at NVIDIA), the work they do, and what kinds of students NVIDIA is looking for across teams, then host an open-ended Q&A. He will also cover how AI is being incorporated across NVIDIA and how software engineers work on hardware problems.\\n\\nBonus: David plans to give away a few prizes, including a GPU and an NVIDIA Jetson kit, as a personal alumni gift. He will announce during the talk how winners will be decided.\\n\\nView more info here -> https://utgracs.github.io/nvidia-gracs-2026/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
